title: Fraternitas Saturni - Blaetter fuer angewandte okkulte Lebenskun
description:
Fraternitas Saturni was the most well known magical order in the western civilization. Through the years 1950 - 1963 the order gave out a magazine called "Blaetter fuer angewandte okkulte Lebenskunst". With over 3500 pages it is the most advanced magical puclication in the world. The language is german.
